# Monitor Control Plane Overhead in Runtime

First, on the main node, clone this repository: `git clone https://github.com/aliceziyun/meshtrek.git`, and change dir to the project's root directory

## Deploy Hotel-Reservation
Execute script `./setup/benchmark/HotelReserve/launch_hotel.sh`, this will automatically set up the Hotel-Reservation application under `hotel` namespace

## Deploy Promethus
Run `./setup/environment/promethus/download_promethus.sh` on main node. 
Run `kubectl get pod -n hotel` to make sure every node is in running state.

## Start the Experiment
- First We need to find out the best configuration for hotel-reservation without service mesh.